-- Nigeria's Diamond Bank seeks approval for up to $400 mln rights issue
-- By Chijioke Ohuocha
-- Wed May 21, 2014 11:25AM EDT
-- None



LAGOS, May 21 (Reuters) - Nigeria's Diamond Bank <DIAMONB.LG> is filing for regulatory approval to raise between $300 million and $400 million via a rights issue from existing shareholders, its chief finance officer told Reuters on Wednesday.

